  <entry>
    <title>异乡与友小聚</title>
    <link href="https://ruopuzi.github.io/2020/06/10/poem-friends/"/>
    <id>https://ruopuzi.github.io/2020/06/10/poem-friends/</id>
    <published>2020-06-10T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-10T04:05:18.735Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>草长莺飞处，<br>蒹葭余落晖。<br>犹忆少年事，<br>情切忘岁催。<br>乡音谈笑足，<br>未曾把酒归。<br>异乡漂泊客，<br>寂寞有人陪。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;草长莺飞处，&lt;br&gt;蒹葭余落晖。&lt;br&gt;犹忆少年事，&lt;br&gt;情切忘岁催。&lt;br&gt;乡音谈笑足，&lt;br&gt;未曾把酒归。&lt;br&gt;异乡漂泊客，&lt;br&gt;寂寞有人陪。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

      
    
    </summary>
    
