  <entry>
    <title>夜宿山中</title>
    <link href="https://ruopuzi.github.io/2020/06/10/poem-live-in-mountain/"/>
    <id>https://ruopuzi.github.io/2020/06/10/poem-live-in-mountain/</id>
    <published>2020-06-10T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-10T04:08:57.726Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>夜半不眠邀清风，<br>贪凉好逸坐山中。<br>星汉无言随夜转，<br>却将流萤作流星。<br>远山似漆露风骨，<br>浮云轻窈却无形。<br>夜虽过半哈欠多，<br>怎可舍此去梦中？</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;夜半不眠邀清风，&lt;br&gt;贪凉好逸坐山中。&lt;br&gt;星汉无言随夜转，&lt;br&gt;却将流萤作流星。&lt;br&gt;远山似漆露风骨，&lt;br&gt;浮云轻窈却无形。&lt;br&gt;夜虽过半哈欠多，&lt;br&gt;怎可舍此去梦中？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;



      
    
