    <title>如梦歌</title>
    <link href="https://ruopuzi.github.io/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/"/>
    <id>https://ruopuzi.github.io/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/</id>
    <published>2019-03-13T08:34:27.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-10T04:00:39.953Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>人生如梦似幻，<br>长短不过百年。<br>少壮盛气凌人，<br>老耋涕泪满面。<br>何不得失两忘，<br>带笑风轻云淡。<br>生时和光同尘，<br>弃执弃妄弃慢。<br>死后身归草木，<br>与尔同游轩辕。</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/13/poem-life-like-dream/1.jpg">]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;人生如梦似幻，&lt;br&gt;长短不过百年。&lt;br&gt;少壮盛气凌人，&lt;br&gt;老耋涕泪满面。&lt;br&gt;何不得失两忘，&lt;br&gt;带笑风轻云淡。&lt;br&gt;生时和光同尘，&lt;br&gt;弃执弃妄弃慢。&lt;br&gt;死后身归草木，&lt;br&gt;与尔同游轩辕。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
      
    
    </summary>
    
